cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.SY. 

The paper discusses an autonomous robot that must take actions to observe its environment and react to unexpected observations, which is a common problem in robotics. The paper also presents an online planning and execution system for robots faced with these challenges. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques to solve the problem. Computer vision (cs.CV) is also relevant as the robot needs to observe its environment. Finally, control systems (cs.SY) are also relevant as the robot needs to adjust its actions based on its observations.
